            <img src="../assets/images/o2o-beauty-booking/o2o-as-is-layout.png" alt="AS‑IS Watsons beauty booking layout with region buttons and chat CTAs" data-full="../assets/images/o2o-beauty-booking/o2o-as-is-layout.png" />
            <figcaption>AS‑IS — Region‑based landing and WhatsApp CTAs led to manual coordination and drop‑offs.</figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
