      <section id="flow" class="section" data-reveal>
        <h2>🧭 Experience flow</h2>
        <ol class="steps">
          <li><strong>Discover</strong>: Choose service → store → date with live slot preview.</li>
          <li><strong>Build</strong>: Select add‑ons with duration and price auto‑recalculated.</li>
          <li><strong>Commit</strong>: Slot is soft‑locked for 5 minutes with countdown; quick auth via OTP/FaceID.</li>
          <li><strong>Confirm</strong>: Pay now or at store; get QR code, calendar event, and reminders.</li>
          <li><strong>Manage</strong>: Reschedule/cancel within policy; changes propagate to therapist schedule.</li>
          <li><strong>In‑store</strong>: Scan membership or QR to check in; status syncs to device.</li>
        </ol>
        <div class="before-after">
          <div>
            <h3>Before</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Unclear slot reliability; double‑booking risk.</li>
              <li>Add‑on impacts hidden until late.</li>
              <li>Weak handoff between online and store.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>After</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Real‑time slots + soft‑lock with countdown.</li>
              <li>Transparent duration and pricing.</li>
              <li>QR check‑in and live schedule sync.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

