      <section id="final-design" class="section" data-reveal>
        <h2>🌟 Final design</h2>
        <p>I didn't just redesign the look — I redesigned the feeling. That's what this new design does.</p>
        <div class="grid two">
          <div class="callout">
            <h3 class="chip-red">Colour Tone</h3>
            <p>The use of a dark background with vibrant accents (pink, purple, mint green) creates a modern, sophisticated aesthetic. The contrast improves readability and draws attention to key elements like service categories and CTAs. The palette aligns with beauty trends, evoking luxury and care, while maintaining accessibility.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="callout">
            <h3 class="chip-red">Patterns & Imagery</h3>
            <p>High‑quality images of beauty products, tools, and models add emotional resonance. Soft‑edged shapes and circular motifs (e.g., eye‑makeup and eyebrow sections) make the layout feel inviting and approachable—ideal for a beauty‑focused platform.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="callout">
            <h3 class="chip-red">Arrangement & Hierarchy</h3>
            <p>Vertical stacking of sections (Beauty Service → Beauty Class → Professional Beauty Service) builds a clear information hierarchy from general to specific. New modules—blog, beauty profile, AI product recommendation—appear near the end so they're discoverable without distracting from the primary booking flow.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="callout">
            <h3 class="chip-red">Flow, trust, and transparency</h3>
            <ul class="bullets">
              <li>Shifted from region chat CTAs to an <strong>in‑site multi‑step flow</strong> (service → location → artist → date) with a <strong>progress header</strong>.</li>
              <li>Added <strong>real‑time slotting</strong> with a <strong>soft‑lock countdown</strong> to prevent double‑booking and reduce anxiety.</li>
              <li>Made <strong>duration and price</strong> recalculation visible when add‑ons change; enabled <strong>back‑to‑back multi‑service</strong> booking with buffers.</li>
              <li>Clarified <strong>cancellation/no‑show policy</strong> inline pre‑confirm and added <strong>QR check‑in</strong> for O+O handoff.</li>
              <li>Integrated <strong>Watsons AR beauty tools</strong> and a structured results UI to connect services with retail.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="callout" style="margin-top:16px;">
            <h3 class="chip-pp">New Features Rationale</h3>
            <ul class="bullets">
              <li><strong>Blog Session</strong> — Educational content builds trust and engagement; tips and trends encourage deeper exploration.</li>
              <li><strong>Interactive AR & AI Tools</strong> — Personalized try‑ons and saved preferences increase retention and make the journey fun and tailored.</li>
              <li><strong>AI Product Recommendation</strong> — Suggests products based on needs or history, streamlining decisions and boosting attach rates.</li>
              <li><strong>Typography and Spacing</strong> — Clean, legible fonts and generous spacing reduce cognitive load for faster decisions.</li>
              <li><strong>Call‑to‑Action (CTA)</strong> — Consistent placement and contrasting "galaxy" styling keeps next actions obvious.</li>
            </ul>
